## Contributing

These skills were built and tested using the [skill-creator](https://docs.claude.ai) workflow — running test prompts with and without the skill, grading outputs, and iterating until the difference was clear.

If you want to adapt a skill for a different discipline (motion design, brand strategy, UX research, etc.): edit the content pillars and context-gathering questions in `SKILL.md`, then test a few real prompts against it and without it. The structure is the same across all skills.

Pull requests welcome.

